data.description: Offering a beautifully remodeled 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom house perched on a hilltop with incredible views.  This home has been remodeled with a brand new kitchen including all new stainless steel appliances.Brand new tile and carpet throughout the home.The roof was replaced approximately 5 years ago and the gutters are brand new.New water heater.New sliding glass doors.Don't forget that the deck nearly wraps around the entire house giving you some amazing outdoor living areas.There is ample room on the side of the house and in the rear to park boats, campers or trailers.No HOA!This home truly is a gem - a must see!
